15
00:02:02.500 --> 00:02:06.000
Key areas of the draft guidance include how the FedRAMP Program would:

16
00:02:06.500 --> 00:02:12.000
Become a security-first program where the security and protection of sensitive data and systems is prioritized above all else. 

17
00:02:12.500 --> 00:02:22.000
Scale the number of FedRAMP authorizations by bringing agencies together to evaluate the security of cloud offerings and strongly incentivizing reuse of one FedRAMP authorization by multiple agencies.

18
00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:29.500
and Streamline the authorization process by automating FedRAMP assessments and processes, consistent with industry best practices. 

